	(btk_tree_view_dy_to_top_row): refactored to use
	btk_tree_view_set_top_row().
	(btk_tree_view_top_row_to_dy): make sure dy >= 0 when done.
	(btk_tree_view_adjustment_changed): only update our dy and
	top_row if the adjustment's dy actually changed.

